  "detailed_description": "<h1>Early Access Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/e50a129fef3866f98693ffb9b5b3521f.avif?t=1736421224\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras_big/e50a129fef3866f98693ffb9b5b3521f.avif?t=1736421224 width=800 height=362 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Native Isekai Defense</strong> takes place in a world called Lumina. Hundreds of years ago, those who called themselves the Progenitors introduced themselves on the world stage. With armies of monsters under their command, the world of Lumina was plunged into an endless great war. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Centuries passed, the Progenitors and their monster armies managed to conquer and contaminate one-third of the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, hope was not yet lost. The genius alchemist, Ariel, succeeded in creating the Ethereal Nexus, an artifact capable of purifying the land of Lumina that had been contaminated by monsters. With this creation, the time to strike back had arrived.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thus, Project Eden was launched. The Pioneer Corps was formed to go forth and reclaim the lands that had been contaminated!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pioneer Corps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the Pioneer Corps alongside other players and become an elite soldier of Lumina! Form parties with various characters and take on different missions!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/2e9fda71865996148dbb584c2a8b0c84.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/2e9fda71865996148dbb584c2a8b0c84.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/2e9fda71865996148dbb584c2a8b0c84.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Project Eden</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The time has come to reclaim the lands of Lumina! Activate the Ethereal Nexus in the corrupted lands and protect it from monster attacks until the land is fully purified!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/20b194fbd79c4720ee7396eafb72adaf.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/20b194fbd79c4720ee7396eafb72adaf.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/20b194fbd79c4720ee7396eafb72adaf.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create the Perfect Defense </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build barricades and towers to help protect the Ethereal Nexus! Create the ultimate defense that enemies cannot penetrate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/d6e3fef0bdc0b8ff9b675d62ab5009ea.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/d6e3fef0bdc0b8ff9b675d62ab5009ea.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/d6e3fef0bdc0b8ff9b675d62ab5009ea.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Catalyst! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strengthen your character with a random Catalyst at the end of each Wave! Choose the combination of catalysts that suits your playstyle and protect the Ethereal Nexus to the last drop of your blood.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/dc2f36cdf24395d66b3e804b38cce501.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/dc2f36cdf24395d66b3e804b38cce501.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/dc2f36cdf24395d66b3e804b38cce501.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Watch Out for Friendly Fire!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch every move you make! Look around—are your allies nearby? Make sure you don’t hurt them! But if it happens, remember, this is war! Friendly fire is inevitable! There is no war without sacrifice!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/a64638793ce49d471800fe882c64da6f.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/a64638793ce49d471800fe882c64da6f.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/a64638793ce49d471800fe882c64da6f.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become a Hero!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In every mission, you will charge into enemy-occupied territory! Use your skills and weapons, and fight alongside your comrades! Protect the Ethereal Nexus with your life, or the life of your comrades! Survive and reclaim our land! And become a hero of Lumina!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/642e1049fcef22e38318b63bc5234ce0.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/642e1049fcef22e38318b63bc5234ce0.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/642e1049fcef22e38318b63bc5234ce0.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Waves of Monsters!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An endless onslaught of monsters! And there’s a big boss too?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Still, you must survive! Even if it means stepping over the lives of your comrades!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the future! Let’s reclaim and free our land from their filthy hands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/870a6278621f8960931ca6fa37070ed1.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/870a6278621f8960931ca6fa37070ed1.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/870a6278621f8960931ca6fa37070ed1.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Native Isekai Defense</strong> takes place in a world called Lumina. Hundreds of years ago, those who called themselves the Progenitors introduced themselves on the world stage. With armies of monsters under their command, the world of Lumina was plunged into an endless great war. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Centuries passed, the Progenitors and their monster armies managed to conquer and contaminate one-third of the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, hope was not yet lost. The genius alchemist, Ariel, succeeded in creating the Ethereal Nexus, an artifact capable of purifying the land of Lumina that had been contaminated by monsters. With this creation, the time to strike back had arrived.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thus, Project Eden was launched. The Pioneer Corps was formed to go forth and reclaim the lands that had been contaminated!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pioneer Corps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the Pioneer Corps alongside other players and become an elite soldier of Lumina! Form parties with various characters and take on different missions!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/2e9fda71865996148dbb584c2a8b0c84.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/2e9fda71865996148dbb584c2a8b0c84.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/2e9fda71865996148dbb584c2a8b0c84.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Project Eden</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The time has come to reclaim the lands of Lumina! Activate the Ethereal Nexus in the corrupted lands and protect it from monster attacks until the land is fully purified!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/20b194fbd79c4720ee7396eafb72adaf.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/20b194fbd79c4720ee7396eafb72adaf.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/20b194fbd79c4720ee7396eafb72adaf.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create the Perfect Defense </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build barricades and towers to help protect the Ethereal Nexus! Create the ultimate defense that enemies cannot penetrate!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/d6e3fef0bdc0b8ff9b675d62ab5009ea.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/d6e3fef0bdc0b8ff9b675d62ab5009ea.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/d6e3fef0bdc0b8ff9b675d62ab5009ea.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Catalyst! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strengthen your character with a random Catalyst at the end of each Wave! Choose the combination of catalysts that suits your playstyle and protect the Ethereal Nexus to the last drop of your blood.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/dc2f36cdf24395d66b3e804b38cce501.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/dc2f36cdf24395d66b3e804b38cce501.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/dc2f36cdf24395d66b3e804b38cce501.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Watch Out for Friendly Fire!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch every move you make! Look around—are your allies nearby? Make sure you don’t hurt them! But if it happens, remember, this is war! Friendly fire is inevitable! There is no war without sacrifice!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/a64638793ce49d471800fe882c64da6f.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/a64638793ce49d471800fe882c64da6f.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/a64638793ce49d471800fe882c64da6f.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become a Hero!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In every mission, you will charge into enemy-occupied territory! Use your skills and weapons, and fight alongside your comrades! Protect the Ethereal Nexus with your life, or the life of your comrades! Survive and reclaim our land! And become a hero of Lumina!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/642e1049fcef22e38318b63bc5234ce0.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/642e1049fcef22e38318b63bc5234ce0.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/642e1049fcef22e38318b63bc5234ce0.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Waves of Monsters!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An endless onslaught of monsters! And there’s a big boss too?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Still, you must survive! Even if it means stepping over the lives of your comrades!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the future! Let’s reclaim and free our land from their filthy hands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/870a6278621f8960931ca6fa37070ed1.poster.avif?t=1736421224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/870a6278621f8960931ca6fa37070ed1.webm?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185770/extras/870a6278621f8960931ca6fa37070ed1.mp4?t=1736421224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
